WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.000
{\an8}<b><font color="#9CD5FF">One Pace Premium</font></b>
Keep the project alive: <font color="#a8c7fa">ko-fi.com/not6ip</font>

2
00:01:42.280 --> 00:01:51.750
♪ Ship! Ship! Ship! Ship! ♪

3
00:01:48.120 --> 00:01:51.710
0 and 4

4
00:02:07.540 --> 00:02:11.420
By the way, have you ever read the WEN?

5
00:02:11.420 --> 00:02:15.680
The WEN, you know? 
The World Economy Newspaper?

6
00:02:15.680 --> 00:02:17.420
You know it, don't you?

7
00:02:18.380 --> 00:02:21.240
There was this comic strip in the WEN!

8
00:02:21.240 --> 00:02:25.700
A giant dreamlike robot was featured in it!
Sora, Warrior of the Sea!

9
00:02:26.300 --> 00:02:28.790
I've been constantly reading it!

10
00:02:28.790 --> 00:02:31.690
Sora, a hero who can walk on water,

11
00:02:31.690 --> 00:02:35.170
accompanied by a 
transforming robot and a seagull,

12
00:02:35.170 --> 00:02:41.390
fights the evil armies of Germa 66.
It's a story of a marine hero!

13
00:02:41.390 --> 00:02:43.720
It has fans all over the world!

14
00:02:43.720 --> 00:02:50.770
I heard it's based on true
stories of Navy heroes.

15
00:02:50.810 --> 00:02:58.740
"Navy"

16
00:02:51.240 --> 00:02:54.480
So it's sort of educational
material to brainwash children!

17
00:02:54.480 --> 00:02:57.690
To teach them that "the Navy is
always right and strong"!

18
00:02:58.690 --> 00:03:02.450
But that's not what I like about it!

19
00:03:02.450 --> 00:03:06.080
It's Germa! Germa 66!

20
00:03:06.080 --> 00:03:11.290
Their evil army always corners Sora
by all possible means!

21
00:03:11.290 --> 00:03:14.170
They're evil heroes!

22
00:03:17.090 --> 00:03:20.140
Yes, they get defeated for the
sake of the story every time,

23
00:03:20.140 --> 00:03:22.890
but I've always supported them
with a white-knuckled intensity!

24
00:03:22.890 --> 00:03:25.430
I supported you guys!

25
00:03:25.430 --> 00:03:28.810
Don't include me!
I have nothing to do with them!

26
00:03:31.260 --> 00:03:36.440
Don't say such a thing!
I'm kind of happy to see you in person, actually!

27
00:03:36.440 --> 00:03:38.790
Why don't you tell that to them?

28
00:03:44.920 --> 00:03:46.450
Hey, open!

29
00:03:49.240 --> 00:03:51.370
♪ Door! ♪

30
00:03:59.320 --> 00:04:01.170
Listen...

31
00:04:01.170 --> 00:04:04.550
Stop following me!
I thought this was my room!

32
00:04:05.180 --> 00:04:09.470
This room belongs to me, too!
Let me out! Dammit!

33
00:04:09.470 --> 00:04:14.400
Why are you treating me so poorly?!
I'm a genius scientist!

34
00:04:14.400 --> 00:04:17.210
Haven't you given up yet?!

35
00:04:17.780 --> 00:04:21.650
We were only told to capture you, Caesar!

36
00:04:21.650 --> 00:04:25.180
But he is the precious groom who will

37
00:04:25.180 --> 00:04:29.290
connect the Vinsmoke family
and us, the Charlotte family!

38
00:04:29.290 --> 00:04:31.480
You two are different in value.

39
00:04:33.460 --> 00:04:37.040
I'm not gonna get married.
Just get out.

40
00:04:37.040 --> 00:04:38.630
"Get out"?!

41
00:04:39.750 --> 00:04:43.720
He's just being mean to Vito!

42
00:04:41.630 --> 00:04:45.130
Gotti "the Hitman"
The Fire Tank Pirates

43
00:04:45.130 --> 00:04:47.640
I can't stand it! Apologize to him!

44
00:04:47.640 --> 00:04:50.140
Gotti! Whoa, wait! Wait!

45
00:04:50.140 --> 00:04:52.210
He hasn't been that mean to me!

46
00:04:52.210 --> 00:04:56.400
I'm okay. Thanks. We were
just messing around.

47
00:04:56.400 --> 00:04:58.520
I wasn't.

48
00:04:59.520 --> 00:05:03.150
Gotti. I want both you and Vito out!

49
00:05:03.150 --> 00:05:06.210
Oh, you said it again!
You're a dead man!

50
00:05:06.210 --> 00:05:08.200
No, Gotti!

51
00:05:08.200 --> 00:05:09.520
Say whatever you like!

52
00:05:09.520 --> 00:05:12.460
But I can't tolerate anyone
who insults my friends!

53
00:05:12.460 --> 00:05:16.170
I said "Wait"! Please don't do it!

54
00:05:17.210 --> 00:05:19.130
You don't have to tolerate me.

55
00:05:19.130 --> 00:05:21.960
It's not like I wanna be your friend.

56
00:05:21.960 --> 00:05:24.180
Son of a...

57
00:05:24.180 --> 00:05:26.520
Gotti!

58
00:05:33.100 --> 00:05:36.390
What are you doing?!

59
00:05:39.120 --> 00:05:40.650
Ma'am!

60
00:05:55.750 --> 00:06:00.290
Do you know that he's Vinsmoke's son?!

61
00:06:01.340 --> 00:06:03.500
If you lay so much as a finger on him,

62
00:06:03.500 --> 00:06:09.090
Father's head will roll!
Don't you get it?! Huh?!

63
00:06:11.930 --> 00:06:15.640
Do you want me to chop 
your head off first, you dummy?!

64
00:06:15.640 --> 00:06:19.980
Ouch! I'm sorry! Ma'am! I'm sorry!

65
00:06:19.980 --> 00:06:21.900
Hey, you...

66
00:06:22.690 --> 00:06:23.940
Ow, ow, ow!

67
00:06:23.940 --> 00:06:26.650
I'm sorry! Ma'am! I'm sorry!

68
00:06:26.650 --> 00:06:29.200
No food for you today as punishment!

69
00:06:29.200 --> 00:06:31.820
No, please, ma'am!

70
00:06:34.880 --> 00:06:40.420
Sorry to bother you.
Let me hear about Germa some other time...

71
00:06:40.420 --> 00:06:41.880
Nope.

72
00:06:51.010 --> 00:06:52.470
Well...

73
00:06:55.750 --> 00:06:58.310
She resembles her...

74
00:07:07.190 --> 00:07:12.200
A Few Days Later...

75
00:07:08.740 --> 00:07:13.200
I can't take it anymore... I'm gonna die...

76
00:07:12.320 --> 00:07:16.990
On the
Thousand Sunny

77
00:07:13.200 --> 00:07:18.290
It's hot... I'm gonna die...

78
00:07:32.290 --> 00:07:36.600
I can't stand the heat...
I wish I could take off this fur skin...

79
00:07:36.600 --> 00:07:41.310
We're like you...
We Minks have low tolerance for heat.

80
00:07:41.310 --> 00:07:45.830
It's really hot.
I'm gonna become a mummy...

81
00:07:45.830 --> 00:07:47.800
A mummy...

82
00:07:47.800 --> 00:07:49.130
A mummy?

83
00:07:49.690 --> 00:07:54.070
A mummy! Nami-san, if I become a mummy,

84
00:07:54.070 --> 00:07:56.490
I'd be a little more alive, right?

85
00:07:55.780 --> 00:07:56.490
I don't care!

86
00:07:56.490 --> 00:08:00.810
In that case, may I see your panties?

87
00:08:00.810 --> 00:08:03.600
I have no energy even to smack you.

88
00:08:03.600 --> 00:08:07.800
Nami, I'm so hungry and it's hot...

89
00:08:07.800 --> 00:08:09.960
I need nutrition...

90
00:08:09.960 --> 00:08:14.810
We're out of food and we couldn't fish
because it'd been stormy for days

91
00:08:14.810 --> 00:08:16.430
and finally it's clear.

92
00:08:16.430 --> 00:08:20.980
Catch some fish somehow
before the weather changes!

93
00:08:20.980 --> 00:08:24.180
We're all gonna starve to death
before we get there!

94
00:08:24.180 --> 00:08:26.840
Food...

95
00:08:27.310 --> 00:08:30.230
We wanna do so, but Nami...

96
00:08:34.240 --> 00:08:38.480
The water is boiling because it's too hot!

97
00:08:38.480 --> 00:08:40.200
What?!

98
00:08:40.200 --> 00:08:43.120
There won't be any fish around then.

99
00:08:43.120 --> 00:08:45.540
What should we do?!

100
00:08:49.620 --> 00:08:51.400
Emergency food...

101
00:08:51.400 --> 00:08:53.380
Don't look at me!

102
00:08:55.930 --> 00:08:58.460
Luffy! You got a bite!

103
00:09:05.060 --> 00:09:07.560
There's a fish! It's huge!

104
00:09:26.920 --> 00:09:30.490
– Pull it up, Luffy!
– Luffy-san, go...

105
00:09:32.800 --> 00:09:34.880
You can do it, Luffy!

106
00:09:34.880 --> 00:09:36.720
Food...

107
00:09:47.600 --> 00:09:50.690
Food!

108
00:09:50.690 --> 00:09:52.520
He did it!

109
00:09:53.180 --> 00:09:54.190
Luffy!

110
00:09:55.570 --> 00:09:57.990
It's very big!

111
00:09:57.990 --> 00:10:01.510
Let's eat!

112
00:10:07.290 --> 00:10:08.710
I did it!

113
00:10:09.580 --> 00:10:12.120
Its color doesn't seem right.

114
00:10:12.600 --> 00:10:14.170
Is it okay to eat?

115
00:10:14.170 --> 00:10:16.480
What are you saying?!
There's no such thing as an inedible fish!

116
00:10:16.480 --> 00:10:19.520
Luffy! Wait a sec!
I'll go check real quick!

117
00:10:19.520 --> 00:10:21.140
What?

118
00:10:24.510 --> 00:10:26.900
Where's the encyclopedia of fish?!

119
00:10:26.900 --> 00:10:29.520
Sanji's bookshelf is full of nudity!

120
00:10:30.360 --> 00:10:31.650
Found it!

121
00:10:31.650 --> 00:10:32.920
Alright.

122
00:10:32.920 --> 00:10:35.920
No, this is not it.

123
00:10:36.690 --> 00:10:37.990
Here it is!

124
00:10:38.530 --> 00:10:43.120
Luffy! Watch out for its skin!
The skin of that fish is extremely poisonous!

125
00:10:43.120 --> 00:10:45.040
Look! I found Sanji's note!

126
00:10:45.040 --> 00:10:46.660
The skin tastes good!

127
00:10:48.040 --> 00:10:50.920
Luffy! Wait! I'll grill it for you!

128
00:10:50.920 --> 00:10:53.300
Here, try it, Carrot.

129
00:10:53.300 --> 00:10:55.920
The skin's so slimy...

130
00:10:55.920 --> 00:10:57.300
Luffy!

131
00:11:03.520 --> 00:11:07.560
– Shall we eat too?
– Yes!

132
00:11:07.560 --> 00:11:12.230
It's delicious! It's so delicious, Nami!

133
00:11:12.230 --> 00:11:16.820
– Yes, it even makes me cry!
– I'm so happy to be alive! Grr!

134
00:11:16.820 --> 00:11:18.360
It's so good!

135
00:11:20.030 --> 00:11:22.770
I just cooked it like it
said in Sanji-kun's note.

136
00:11:26.360 --> 00:11:30.540
Chopper, you need energy too, first.
Eat it.

137
00:11:35.090 --> 00:11:39.760
Luffy's gonna... d-die!

138
00:11:39.760 --> 00:11:42.590
I-It's cold...

139
00:11:44.800 --> 00:11:46.940
Crying isn't gonna help!

140
00:11:46.940 --> 00:11:51.720
Here! To take care of Luffy,
you have to gain energy, Chopper!

141
00:11:51.720 --> 00:11:53.400
Now, eat!

142
00:11:53.400 --> 00:11:54.690
Okay!

143
00:11:56.480 --> 00:12:02.770
But even if I wanna treat him,
we're short of antidotal herbs!

144
00:12:08.400 --> 00:12:09.830
Yum!

145
00:12:09.830 --> 00:12:12.730
We gotta find an island, Nami!

146
00:12:17.180 --> 00:12:20.240
We're lacking herbs!

147
00:12:21.920 --> 00:12:22.800
Yum!

148
00:12:24.760 --> 00:12:26.800
Food...

149
00:12:28.850 --> 00:12:32.460
But it's not that easy to find an island...

150
00:12:32.920 --> 00:12:35.060
Sanji-kun's encyclopedia says
it's extremely poisonous

151
00:12:35.060 --> 00:12:38.730
and kills you instantly if
you eat the skin, right?

152
00:12:38.730 --> 00:12:39.980
Yeah.

153
00:12:39.980 --> 00:12:40.820
Yum!

154
00:12:40.820 --> 00:12:45.440
But he's still alive!
Doesn't that mean he has strong antibodies?

155
00:12:45.440 --> 00:12:48.430
He has one of the best vital powers
of all humankind!

156
00:12:48.430 --> 00:12:50.730
But he's in very bad shape!

157
00:12:54.060 --> 00:12:55.620
Yum!

158
00:12:56.520 --> 00:12:59.380
Luffy, are you okay?

159
00:13:01.080 --> 00:13:04.220
The river is... beautiful...

160
00:13:04.220 --> 00:13:06.550
He's seeing the River Styx!

161
00:13:09.040 --> 00:13:12.930
We're about to reach Mama's territory.

162
00:13:17.020 --> 00:13:22.280
There are some islands in the area
around Whole Cake Island.

163
00:13:22.760 --> 00:13:26.740
I'd say Black Leg and the others
have passed through those islands

164
00:13:26.740 --> 00:13:29.880
and reached Whole Cake Island by now.

165
00:13:38.300 --> 00:13:41.580
Don't lower your guard, guys...

166
00:13:42.170 --> 00:13:43.920
I'll stand guard!

167
00:13:45.340 --> 00:13:50.490
I was gonna stop by at the first island.
Let's get an antidote there.

168
00:13:50.490 --> 00:13:51.510
Okay.

169
00:13:56.160 --> 00:13:58.980
What? This time, it's snow?

170
00:13:59.610 --> 00:14:01.400
It's beautiful!

171
00:14:01.400 --> 00:14:04.990
It's not snow! Are those clouds of sugar?!

172
00:14:04.990 --> 00:14:09.240
That's right.
And it's a cotton candy flurry that's falling.

173
00:14:09.240 --> 00:14:11.830
What?! Cotton candy?!

174
00:14:14.410 --> 00:14:15.850
Nice! Nice!

175
00:14:19.180 --> 00:14:20.250
Sweet...

176
00:14:28.180 --> 00:14:30.140
Territorial
Sea Slug

177
00:14:34.700 --> 00:14:37.720
Oh? Who is it?

178
00:14:37.720 --> 00:14:41.770
Your transponder snail is 
receiving warning signals.

179
00:14:41.770 --> 00:14:47.610
That means we're 
in Big Mom's territory for sure.

180
00:14:47.610 --> 00:14:49.070
Cotton candy!

181
00:14:49.530 --> 00:14:52.950
Guys! Hide or disguise yourselves!

182
00:14:52.950 --> 00:14:54.480
So sweet!

183
00:14:55.520 --> 00:14:57.450
Are you listening?!

184
00:15:02.080 --> 00:15:04.250
I see something, Pekoms!

185
00:15:06.840 --> 00:15:10.010
It's a ship! A ship is coming towards us!

186
00:15:10.010 --> 00:15:14.050
What?! Are they here already?!

187
00:15:15.060 --> 00:15:15.940
What do you mean?!

188
00:15:15.940 --> 00:15:20.140
– That's probably a tarte, one of our scout ships.
– What?!

189
00:15:21.000 --> 00:15:24.730
– I can't see it clearly because of the fog.
– What should we do?

190
00:15:24.730 --> 00:15:28.860
– I'll handle it somehow, so all of you, go hide!
– Got it!

191
00:15:28.860 --> 00:15:32.820
– Oh, no! Luffy is looking really sick!
– What?!

192
00:15:32.820 --> 00:15:34.800
The poison must've spread
into his system even more!

193
00:15:34.800 --> 00:15:38.450
It's dangerous! We gotta treat him ASAP!

194
00:15:38.450 --> 00:15:41.160
Don't they have an antidote
on that scout ship?!

195
00:15:41.160 --> 00:15:45.170
– I'll ask them for you! Hurry up and hide!
– Okay!

196
00:15:45.880 --> 00:15:48.040
Chopper-san, hurry up!

197
00:16:00.230 --> 00:16:01.140
What?!

198
00:16:26.300 --> 00:16:27.840
Luffy...

199
00:16:49.900 --> 00:16:51.740
Is that a transponder snail?

200
00:16:51.740 --> 00:16:53.700
It's huge!

201
00:16:54.240 --> 00:16:56.200
There is a number.

202
00:16:57.340 --> 00:16:59.280
Sixty-six?

203
00:17:02.980 --> 00:17:07.540
This is Germa.
Is that the Straw Hats' ship?

204
00:17:07.540 --> 00:17:09.960
That's Germa 66's ship!

205
00:17:12.220 --> 00:17:17.720
Germa 66...
The organization led by Sanji-kun's father...

206
00:17:18.270 --> 00:17:22.180
Why are you here, Straw Hats?!

207
00:17:24.430 --> 00:17:28.350
We're gonna collide!
Guys, furl the sail!

208
00:17:30.980 --> 00:17:33.280
Luffy, I'll be back.

209
00:18:05.260 --> 00:18:07.850
We managed to avoid the crash...

210
00:18:08.180 --> 00:18:10.480
Sanji!

211
00:18:10.480 --> 00:18:12.730
Sanji!

212
00:18:14.780 --> 00:18:17.990
Oh, that twirly eyebrow! It's Sanji-san !

213
00:18:17.990 --> 00:18:20.200
What? Sanji? Is that Sanji?!

214
00:18:20.780 --> 00:18:22.330
Sanji!

215
00:18:22.840 --> 00:18:24.620
Sanji-kun !

216
00:18:25.250 --> 00:18:28.500
Great!
I didn't expect to see you this soon!

217
00:18:28.500 --> 00:18:31.040
How lucky we are...

218
00:18:35.170 --> 00:18:40.680
Hey, Sanji! We have a problem!
Luffy got poisoned by eating fish and is dying!

219
00:18:40.680 --> 00:18:43.010
Is there any antidote on that ship?!

220
00:18:43.010 --> 00:18:44.350
Sanji!

221
00:18:45.810 --> 00:18:48.890
Stop calling me "Sanji"!

222
00:18:49.480 --> 00:18:51.190
You got the wrong person!

223
00:18:55.460 --> 00:18:58.180
Well, of course I look like him.

224
00:19:00.110 --> 00:19:02.700
My name is Yonji!

225
00:19:01.950 --> 00:19:06.490
Vinsmoke "Winch Green" Yonji
Germa 66

226
00:19:06.490 --> 00:19:08.330
Yonji?!

227
00:19:08.330 --> 00:19:10.160
Not "San(three)-ji" but "Yon(four)-ji"?!

228
00:19:10.160 --> 00:19:13.340
He resembles him
and has twirly eyebrows but he's not him?!

229
00:19:13.340 --> 00:19:18.620
My relationship with your friend Sanji
is a secret of secrets.

230
00:19:18.620 --> 00:19:22.090
It's absolutely confidential!

231
00:19:22.090 --> 00:19:24.760
He's definitely his younger brother...

232
00:19:26.640 --> 00:19:28.360
So he also had a younger brother...

233
00:19:28.360 --> 00:19:31.230
What?! How can you tell
that's his younger brother?!

234
00:19:33.400 --> 00:19:36.110
Cutie! Cute, so cute...

235
00:19:36.110 --> 00:19:38.780
Are you really not Sanji?!

236
00:19:39.100 --> 00:19:40.450
Your Highness.

237
00:19:41.140 --> 00:19:45.140
I don't think they are transporting
Prince Sanji on that ship.

238
00:19:45.590 --> 00:19:48.120
So I guess we missed each other.

239
00:19:48.120 --> 00:19:53.250
You're right. Let's go back.
It was a wasted trip.

240
00:19:53.250 --> 00:19:55.880
Wait, Sanji!

241
00:19:55.880 --> 00:19:57.170
I'm Yonji!

242
00:19:59.050 --> 00:20:00.800
Oh, Luffy...

243
00:20:03.420 --> 00:20:05.720
A rash is breaking out all over his body!

244
00:20:05.720 --> 00:20:08.180
He's losing his resistance!

245
00:20:08.640 --> 00:20:13.650
This poison is so severe!
Luffy may have strong antibodies, but it's...

246
00:20:17.770 --> 00:20:19.780
Luffy, stay with us!

247
00:20:20.440 --> 00:20:25.450
Hey, it's just fish poison!
I thought you were gonna be the pirate king!

248
00:20:25.450 --> 00:20:27.490
Luffy! Don't die!

249
00:20:27.490 --> 00:20:28.790
Luffy-san !

250
00:20:28.790 --> 00:20:32.790
Hey, please!
I bet you have antidotes!

251
00:20:32.790 --> 00:20:36.080
We used all we got,
but he still needs more!

252
00:20:39.210 --> 00:20:41.050
Hey!

253
00:20:41.050 --> 00:20:45.550
If you're Sanji-san's brother,
please save Luffy-san !

254
00:20:49.620 --> 00:20:55.110
I'm sorry.
I have no interest in saving people.

255
00:20:56.650 --> 00:21:00.880
Or do you wanna try and
rob the medicine from us?

256
00:21:00.880 --> 00:21:03.140
Like pirates?

257
00:21:04.200 --> 00:21:05.260
What a jerk!

258
00:21:05.260 --> 00:21:08.720
He's totally different from Sanji-kun !
Even though he likes girls too!

259
00:21:08.720 --> 00:21:11.240
He's not kind at all!

260
00:21:12.280 --> 00:21:14.580
Just say the word if you want me to kill him!

261
00:21:16.000 --> 00:21:17.170
Yonji.

262
00:21:20.080 --> 00:21:22.630
Stop being so stingy!

263
00:21:27.100 --> 00:21:28.760
Your Highness!

264
00:21:30.390 --> 00:21:32.120
What's going on?!

265
00:21:36.440 --> 00:21:37.770
Luffy!

266
00:21:39.270 --> 00:21:41.320
Oh, Lady Reiju!

267
00:21:46.240 --> 00:21:47.410
Luffy!

268
00:21:49.870 --> 00:21:51.620
Luffy!

269
00:21:54.120 --> 00:21:56.660
– Luffy-san !
– No!

270
00:22:07.620 --> 00:22:09.390
An invader!

271
00:22:09.390 --> 00:22:10.800
Who are you?!

272
00:22:25.070 --> 00:22:29.130
Hello. I'm sorry.

273
00:22:30.030 --> 00:22:36.150
My young brother is a cold-blooded jackass.

274
00:22:43.380 --> 00:22:44.960
Young brother?

275
00:22:44.960 --> 00:22:46.590
Are you his sister?

276
00:22:53.310 --> 00:22:57.580
Vinsmoke "Poison Pink" Reiju
Germa 66

277
00:22:59.520 --> 00:23:01.350
Her eyebrows are twirly too!

278
00:23:01.350 --> 00:23:04.230
She's gorgeous!

279
00:23:07.500 --> 00:23:08.900
Reiju!

280
00:23:08.900 --> 00:23:09.900
Is he flying?!

281
00:23:09.900 --> 00:23:13.530
You bitch!
How could you humiliate me?!

282
00:23:13.530 --> 00:23:15.910
Shut up!
You should be ashamed of yourself!

283
00:23:18.200 --> 00:23:21.250
What? Is he hovering in the air?

284
00:23:21.250 --> 00:23:22.880
It's science!

285
00:23:22.880 --> 00:23:23.750
What?!

286
00:23:24.140 --> 00:23:30.300
Germa 66 is a group of fighters
who have honed themselves with science.

287
00:23:30.300 --> 00:23:33.260
They are a scientific
fighting squad, if you will.

288
00:23:35.560 --> 00:23:37.390
And Mama is...

289
00:23:39.640 --> 00:23:42.690
looking to get that technology!

290
00:23:44.780 --> 00:23:49.280
Pekoms-san, if I'm correct,
Vinsmoke was...

291
00:23:49.280 --> 00:23:52.490
the name of a royal family, wasn't it?

292
00:23:54.740 --> 00:23:58.310
If I remember right, it was a family that

293
00:23:58.310 --> 00:24:02.120
conquered the North Blue
by force of arms long ago!

294
00:24:02.620 --> 00:24:07.090
By "royal family,"
you mean like Vivi and Neptune?!

295
00:24:07.090 --> 00:24:09.800
What? Are they such a prominent family?

296
00:24:09.800 --> 00:24:14.310
That's right. They were synonymous
with "evil" in a past age.

297
00:24:14.310 --> 00:24:17.930
That's why they were used as
models for the comic strip.

298
00:24:18.340 --> 00:24:21.270
Skeleton-san,
you have so much historical knowledge.

299
00:24:21.270 --> 00:24:23.310
I've lived a long time...

300
00:24:23.310 --> 00:24:25.020
I'm dead now though.

301
00:24:25.020 --> 00:24:32.110
But it's not just a story from the past.
We're still a royal family.

302
00:24:32.530 --> 00:24:35.300
Germa is a country without soil.

303
00:24:35.300 --> 00:24:40.410
We have no land to govern,
but we're given the right to attend the Reverie.

304
00:24:40.410 --> 00:24:43.750
Oh, I beg your pardon.

305
00:24:45.630 --> 00:24:50.340
If that is so, may I see your panties?

306
00:24:51.420 --> 00:24:52.880
Stop it!

307
00:24:59.800 --> 00:25:02.770
Okay, now, can I have it?

308
00:25:04.480 --> 00:25:09.480
Looks like he ate an armored stonefish
from the Boiling Sea, didn't he?

309
00:25:09.480 --> 00:25:11.860
What? How did you know?

310
00:25:11.860 --> 00:25:14.650
The way this poison works is unique.

311
00:25:16.500 --> 00:25:20.240
He must be greedy.
It could even kill a giant instantly.

312
00:25:20.240 --> 00:25:24.790
What?! Oh, no!
Then, there's no way to save Luffy...

313
00:25:26.790 --> 00:25:30.140
I shouldn't be a ship's doctor anymore!

314
00:25:31.460 --> 00:25:34.470
But this boy is lucky.

315
00:25:34.470 --> 00:25:37.120
Because this poison is...

316
00:25:37.920 --> 00:25:40.680
one of my favorite things!

317
00:25:43.640 --> 00:25:45.640
W-What are you gonna do?

318
00:25:46.590 --> 00:25:48.350
Let's have it!

319
00:25:57.030 --> 00:26:03.200
What?! Whoa! Whoa! Whoa!
If you suck up poison like that, you're gonna die!

320
00:26:03.200 --> 00:26:06.620
Oh! I'm jealous! Smooch!

321
00:26:06.620 --> 00:26:10.840
I wish I could change places with him!
Even though my lips...

322
00:26:10.840 --> 00:26:15.880
are gone!

323
00:26:30.400 --> 00:26:33.270
The rash is transferring to her body!

324
00:26:33.270 --> 00:26:34.320
What?!

325
00:27:05.640 --> 00:27:09.190
The rash on Luffy's body is all gone!

326
00:27:09.190 --> 00:27:12.360
You've sucked it all out?! Are you alright?!

327
00:27:12.360 --> 00:27:16.210
Yes, of course. I'm Poison Pink.

328
00:27:17.320 --> 00:27:18.860
Poison...

329
00:27:18.860 --> 00:27:20.910
...Pink?

330
00:27:26.840 --> 00:27:28.250
It was delicious!

331
00:27:41.020 --> 00:27:42.840
What?! What happened?!

332
00:27:42.840 --> 00:27:46.880
Luffy! Luffy!

333
00:27:47.520 --> 00:27:50.620
– I'm so relieved!
– Are you all right?!

334
00:27:50.620 --> 00:27:52.980
What a relief!

335
00:27:52.980 --> 00:27:55.360
Luffy!

336
00:27:55.360 --> 00:27:59.440
Oh? Did I fall asleep while eating fish?

337
00:27:59.440 --> 00:28:02.360
The skin was so good! Is there any left?

338
00:28:02.360 --> 00:28:06.080
– No! Don't you remember?!
– Nope.

339
00:28:08.490 --> 00:28:09.660
Sanji!

340
00:28:09.660 --> 00:28:11.210
She's a woman!

341
00:28:11.210 --> 00:28:13.290
Oh, right. Who is this?

342
00:28:13.290 --> 00:28:16.390
Luffy-san, she saved your life!

343
00:28:16.390 --> 00:28:20.090
What? Thank you for... what again?

344
00:28:23.550 --> 00:28:26.550
So that's Straw Hat Luffy...

345
00:28:26.550 --> 00:28:30.730
Oh! You're Sanji's sister!

346
00:28:30.730 --> 00:28:31.800
Yes.

347
00:28:32.600 --> 00:28:36.270
Sanji is one of us, the Vinsmoke family.

348
00:28:37.940 --> 00:28:41.100
Our father parted from Sanji
when he was a little kid

349
00:28:41.100 --> 00:28:44.250
and has been looking for him.

350
00:28:44.250 --> 00:28:48.470
When Sanji's wanted poster 
was circulated two years ago,

351
00:28:48.470 --> 00:28:52.290
our father immediately asked 
Navy Headquarters to pursue him.

352
00:28:54.080 --> 00:28:59.000
But they found the wrong man—
someone named Duval.

353
00:28:59.000 --> 00:29:00.500
Duval!

354
00:29:04.100 --> 00:29:08.140
He's the guy from the Flying Fish Riders
who we met before Sabaody...

355
00:29:08.720 --> 00:29:13.180
Oh, I remember!
Sanji-san was mad about it too.

356
00:29:13.810 --> 00:29:18.920
It was only recently
that the government called us saying

357
00:29:18.920 --> 00:29:22.700
that they finally captured an image
of Black Leg Sanji amid the chaos

358
00:29:22.700 --> 00:29:25.240
evoked by the Straw Hats' comeback.

359
00:29:25.950 --> 00:29:29.580
Our father raised the bounty right away

360
00:29:29.580 --> 00:29:33.070
and made them change "DEAD OR ALIVE"...

361
00:29:33.070 --> 00:29:38.080
... to "ONLY ALIVE."

362
00:29:38.080 --> 00:29:42.960
That's why only Sanji-kun's poster was
changed a little bit.

363
00:29:46.380 --> 00:29:50.260
Where is Sanji now?

364
00:29:50.740 --> 00:29:52.010
I don't know.

365
00:29:52.010 --> 00:29:57.270
Maybe he's with Big Mom or with our father.

366
00:29:57.270 --> 00:30:02.020
We came to greet him,
but I think we missed each other.

367
00:30:06.070 --> 00:30:11.800
Well, if he can attend the tea party,
that's all that matters.

368
00:30:11.800 --> 00:30:13.790
And I got to see you guys, too.

369
00:30:16.460 --> 00:30:20.670
Thank you for looking after my brother
all this time.

370
00:30:27.120 --> 00:30:28.340
Sanji's sister!

371
00:30:30.780 --> 00:30:33.510
Thank you for saving my life.

372
00:30:33.880 --> 00:30:35.270
But...

373
00:30:36.480 --> 00:30:41.560
I still want Sanji back! He's my friend!

374
00:31:08.560 --> 00:31:11.050
I'm gonna take back Sanji at any cost!

375
00:31:16.520 --> 00:31:19.890
See? She saved our enemy's life.

376
00:31:22.060 --> 00:31:25.940
Hey, you!
You're Pekoms from the Big Mom Pirates, right?

377
00:31:26.860 --> 00:31:30.030
Why are you with the Straw Hats?

378
00:31:31.450 --> 00:31:38.200
I have my own reason!
Why do I have to explain it to you guys?!

379
00:31:39.410 --> 00:31:45.000
There's no bond between us yet!

380
00:31:45.000 --> 00:31:46.590
You're right!

381
00:31:52.600 --> 00:31:56.580
I'll pretend that I didn't
see anything for now.

382
00:31:56.580 --> 00:32:03.690
Yeah, we don't wanna cause trouble and
break off our brother's marriage.

383
00:32:05.840 --> 00:32:08.360
We'd best all tread lightly.

384
00:32:08.360 --> 00:32:10.610
That'd be smart!

385
00:32:10.610 --> 00:32:13.200
Weigh anchor! Let's go back.

386
00:32:18.450 --> 00:32:21.330
Well, good luck.

387
00:32:48.610 --> 00:32:52.030
They didn't get into a fight with Germa,
it seems.

388
00:32:53.880 --> 00:32:59.040
Yes, I'm sure that's their ship.
Straw Hat Luffy is on board, too.

389
00:33:01.540 --> 00:33:03.250
What do you wanna do...

390
00:33:04.170 --> 00:33:06.340
Jinbe?
